4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that aims to help individuals start a career as a data scientist and build their first ML models. The course is designed for beginners with no previous knowledge required. It lasts for 16 weeks and includes 3 classes weekly with a maximum of 12 people per class. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, statistics, supervised and unsupervised learning models, and more. Students will also practice solving real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The instructors for this course include Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena, who have extensive experience in the field of AI and machine learning. The course offers certificates that are recognized by multiple organizations. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop